title: DHS Issues Memo Ordering The Immediate Construction Of Border Wall
text:
Go to Article 
Two Department of Homeland Security memos signed by DHS director John Kelly and released on Tuesday authorized the implementation of President Donald Trump’s executive orders on illegal immigration and security at the southern border, including building Trump’s proposed border wall.
